parameters:
Lackey: You bastard, not a single keyholder sold? What's the
meaning of this!? Are you even trying to sell seriously!?
Huh!?

Memimi: Hey! Just because they're members absorbed from a
defeated organization, you have no right to hit your
subordinates!! Stop it!

Lackey: Don't act all high and mighty! You're just an
underling like him now. You're not in any position to talk
back, got it?

Memimi: No, I will speak out!! Fighting against injustice is
the essence of a monster! We, the monsters trained by Lord
Shark Broccoli, will not submit to unwarranted violence!

Memimi: Why don't you fight back a little!? It's a duel, a
duel! You can't let yourself be disrespected like this!!
